      "title": "Red Dragon (2002 film)",
      "score": 0.04227946147435349,
      "text": "Red Dragon (2002 film)\nRed Dragon is a 2002 horror film based on the novel of the same title by Thomas Harris. Anthony Hopkins stars as psychiatrist and serial killer Dr. Hannibal Lecter. It is a prequel to The Silence of the Lambs (1991) and Hannibal (2001). The novel was originally adapted into the film Manhunter (1986).",
